Brussel Sprout Coleslaw
via http://www.shutterbean.com/2010/brussels-sprout-salad/

24 Brussels sprouts, washed and dried, woody ends cut off
8 ounces Gruyere cheese, grated fine
6 ounces walnuts, broken into small pieces

Dressing:
3 tablespoons apple cider vinegar
9 tablespoons extra-virgin olive oil
2 teaspoons Dijon mustard 
kosher salt and cracked black pepper

Slice or mandoline the brussel sprouts, roast the walnuts, grate the cheese.  Mix.

Combine dressing ingredients in a small jar, shake, and pour over the rest.  Toss to combine.